<!-- Regressionen auf Carhart's Alpha Teil 1-->
```{r, echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE, results='asis'}

library(stargazer)

stargazer(model1_c,model2_c, header=FALSE, type='latex', model.numbers= FALSE, title = "Four Regression Models Predicting Influence on Alpha Part 1",  column.labels = c("Age", "Age Classes"),omit.stat = c("rsq", "f")
)
```
